wins同五月天嘅target audience係咪類近呢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b788a9240775cfd2d4f55066020b176bbbcc47ed","tid":615712,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T15:46:27.000Z","msg":"其實我有一個問題的<br />\n假如沒有黃牛，咁在職嘅五月天迷係點樣走去聽五月天架呢？<br />\n究竟有無25歲以上嘅fans係不透過黃牛入場架呢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd895db0dd82a31e72c44dfd4082f78b308b354","tid":615712,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b788a9240775cfd2d4f55066020b176bbbcc47ed","tid":615712,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T15:46:27.000Z","msg":"其實我有一個問題的<br />\n假如沒有黃牛，咁在職嘅五月天迷係點樣走去聽五月天架呢？<br />\n究竟有無25歲以上嘅fans係不透過黃牛入場架呢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T15:48:45.000Z","msg":"聽講台灣實名登記，ban晒所有買黃牛嘅人，唔知係個次之後嘅五月天演唱會，觀眾群嘅年齡有無大大減低呢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢d真係非常值得深思嘅經濟議題"},{"pid":"83ae2c1c09d24fe0eac2fbe219fa315ad57c2060","tid":615712,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T16:00:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21f7a7ade15b599986231c99b9edb5185b75943","tid":615712,"uid":532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"83ae2c1c09d24fe0eac2fbe219fa315ad57c2060","tid":615712,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T16:00:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T23:05:47.000Z","msg":"點解要忽略網上訂飛呢個方法？"},{"pid":"fe81376b4263ba41de6e3a59bfc12d4a27c9e627","tid":615712,"uid":142128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T23:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\